        <div class="clearing_fmt"> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
       <p class="aia_read_full_fmt"> <a href="http://www.webmd.com/mental-health/features/is-hypochondria-stressing-your-marriage" onclick="return sl(this,'','aia-related');">Is Hypochondria Stressing Your Marriage?</a> </p> 
       <div class="aia_section_fmt"> 
        <div class="aia_content_fmt"> 
         <p>Sometimes recognizing hypochondria takes a little time. It wasn't until Rebecca Serrano (not her real name) had been married for a full year that she realized her new husband had a problem. Once, he was convinced he had testicular cancer -- but he wouldn't go to the doctor. Another time, when he got a sinus infection, he thought it was a brain tumor. &quot;This anxiety literally led him to feel more pain than a normal person would feel. He had panic attacks and was in such a slump over any minor...</p> 
